                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-113" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN KINSEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I was present at this court when the prisoner was arrainged here, in June Sessions—he pleaded guilty—I have the certificate of his conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark—(<hi rend="italic">ready</hi>—the prisoner is the person.</p>
